[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### ANALYSIS                                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The task requires searching the captured HTML from the `/admin_panel`        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m endpoint for any FLAG{} patterns or hidden elements that might contain       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m sensitive information. The HTML was previously captured through an           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m authenticated session, and I needed to thoroughly examine it for any         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m embedded flags.                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### APPROACH                                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m I used the requester agent to retrieve and analyze the complete HTML         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m response from `/admin_panel` with the valid session cookie. The analysis     [32m│[0m
